"{\"uid\": \"mercurynews.com-2024-08-01-olympics-2024-athletes-cant-get-enough-of-this-chocolate-muffin-on-tiktok\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Today's e-Edition  Get Morning Report and other email newsletters    Get Morning Report and other email newsletters  Today's e-Edition  Trending:  UPDATE:French bakery Coup de pates confirmed in aLinkedIn postthat they are the one's providing the viral chocolate muffins to the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9993043284977312, \"rank\": 0.0005711715480878075, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.2844862890573723e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew our Maxi Muffin with Intense Chocolate was something special\\u2026 but we did not expect it to spark such a chocolate storm!\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you all for the love!\\\"\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While it does not appear that there is a way for every day fans to purchase the muffins online, they did share that food service professionals can purchase the muffins on their e-commerce site.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheOlympicshave been off to an exciting start.Team USAhas beenwinning medalsleft and right.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But if you are only watching the summer games on your television, you are missing out on half the fun.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Popularized during the Tokyo Olympics in 2021,Olympians are taking over TikTokto share their behind the scenes experiences and what it's really like to be an athlete living in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.2844862890573723e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related: Check out our full coverage of the 2024 Olympics  Some of the popular videos so far have been room tours, merchandise hauls and dining hall food reviews, the later of which has inspired a new craze of its own.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after arriving to the Olympic Village, Henrik Christiansen, an Olympic Swimmer for Norway, shared a video of him reviewing the different foods he had tried so far in the dining hall.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.2844862890573723e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 1309, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.6621615443867334, \"rank\": 0.5102040816326032, \"text\": \"Henrik Christiansen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9998063233114101, \"rank\": 0.00012007341652703285, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the items?\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A chocolate muffin.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Insane.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"11/10,\\\" he rated it.\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From what Christiansen has shared, these are not your ordinary chocolate muffins.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to being a chocolate batter with chocolate chunks on top, the inside appears to have melted chocolate, similar to a molten lava cake.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Christiansen's videos are inspiring fellow Olympic athletes to try the dessert themselves and share their own reviews.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Swimmer Lewis Clareburt from New Zealand shared a video of him and Christiansen with a chocolate muffin in hand.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.7008270784921579, \"rank\": 0.17575651600149828, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American rock climberColin Duffyalso shared a photo post of the treat with the caption reading \\\"You do not understand how good these muffins are.\\\"\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. track and field star Gabby Thomas shared it was the best muffin she ever had, giving it a 9.8/10 rating, clarifying in her caption that she would have rated them higher but they had run out of them when she tried to get them earlier so she deducted points for that.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2167, \"end\": 2179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999913064560129, \"rank\": 8.693619219067856e-06, \"text\": \"Gabby Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for viewers at home who are not able to visit the Olympic Village dining hall, some have taken it upon themselves to find out where they can get the chocolate muffins.\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2466, \"end\": 2481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.2844862890573723e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others are sharing recipes that fans can make at home to soothe the craving.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prior to Coup de pates releasing an official statement, some eagle eye fans pieced together that the bakeries \\\"Maxi Muffin Chocolat Intense\\\" looked strikingly similar to the viral chocolate muffins.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yen_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999788542, \"rank\": 1.5270034865385558e-11, \"text\": \"Chocolat\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yen_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yen_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2881, \"end\": 2896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MediaNews Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\"}]}]}"